Package it.cnr.isti.thematrix.scripting.aggregate.support

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregateFunction
    Base class for aggregate functions.
    Avg
    Avg implements the averagig AggregateFunction, it only allows INT and FLOAT types, counts all non-null, non MISSING elements, returns a Float average.
    Count
    Count implements the AggregateFunction counting data rows.
    Max
    Max implements the maximum AggregateFunction, defined on INT, FLOAT and BOOLEAN types only.
    Min
    Min implements the minimum AggregateFunction, defined on INT, FLOAT, DATE and BOOLEAN types only.
    StDev
    StDev implements the standard deviation AggregateFunction, it only allows INT and FLOAT types, counts all non-null, non MISSING elements, returns a Float average.
    Sum
    Sum implements the sum AggregateFunction, only allows INT and FLOAT types.
